These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, skiing, water-polo
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, havana, old-henry
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, traveling, writing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, mystery
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, purple, ivory
House: futuristic, art-deco, gothic-revival
 1. the person watching documentary movies is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6
 2. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 3. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
 4. the person who likes ivory is somewhere between the person who's sport is climbing and the gothic-revival house##7
 5. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is the futuristic house##1
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person who likes purple##6
 8. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the gothic-revival house is not the person who's hobby is writing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |
| Sport      | climbing       | skiing  | water-polo     |
| Cigar          | old-henry       | havana  | ritmeester    |
| Hobby         | card-games  | writing   | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | drama     |
| Color   | ebony  | ivory | purple   |
| House           | art-deco  | futuristic      | gothic-revival  |

