There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, lilac, blue
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, mexican, russian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
 2. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
 3. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 4. the person who likes blue is somewhere between the person traveling to miami and the person who growszinnia##7
 5. the person drinking milk is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
 6. the person who growslily is between the indonesian and the person who likes lilac##2
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
 8. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person who growszinnia and the person drinking cola##7
 9. the mexican is on the far left##1
10. the person traveling to miami is not the indonesian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2        |      3       |
| Flower          | sunflower       | lily         | zinnia         |
| Beverage         | cola  | milk         | hot-chocolate   |
| City           | miami     | paris | london |
| Color   | lilac         | blue         | azure        |
| Nationality   | mexican      | russian        | indonesian   |
| Sport         | snowboarding | volleyball     | soccer       |

