 3. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the person playing go and the person who's birthday is in october##7
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 8. the person driving the trike is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
10. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
11. the ritmeester-smoker is not the person playing mah-jongg##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3      |
