7. the person who's birthday is in august is the townhouse house##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the person eating weightliftingrot and the person drinking lemonade##7
9. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the person eating weightliftingrot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | cola       | iced-tea      | lemonade    |
| Food          | weightliftingrot     | papaya        | kiwi        |
| House           | victorian  | townhouse | gothic-revival   |
| Pet   | frog | chinchilla           | cat |
| Birthday   | june  | august    | september   |
| Sport     | parkour        | soccer          | weightlifting         |

