The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, swimming, volleyball
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, june, october
 1. the accountant is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere between the person who likes emerald and the person who likes yellow##7
 4. the paramedic is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 6. the person who likes light-blue is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the accountant##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person who growslily##5
10. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
11. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the right of the person who likes yellow##5

